{"tid":1597924,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（女user入）有無人食過蘆葦蔥？？","createTime":"2019-09-27T07:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T06:09:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"97129d59ed9946ad9a8d3b4332c1205c0f5cd66e","tid":1597924,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:28:14.000Z","msg":"蘆葦蔥<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aVUdMoQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaVUdMoQ.png&h=a559c3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家食過未???<br />\n<br />\n份量: 6 人份<br />\n時間: 20 分鐘<br />\n<br />\n食材<br />\n蘆葦心1斤<br />\n紅辣椒2根<br />\n山地蔥1把<br />\n絞肉100克<br />\n<br />\n做法:<br />\n1. 蘆葦心取較嫩的部份，用鹽水煮到去掉其苦澀味。<br />\n2. 撈起沖泡冷水，冰鎮一個晚上。<br />\n3. 絞肉、辣椒、山地蔥爆香淋上即可食用。"},{"pid":"901fa721124c74570cd11439e3a5b7f91a3856ed","tid":1597924,"uid":242805,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:37:07.000Z","msg":"一開頭睇以為係講盧偉聰，點知原來真係講蘆葦蔥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b555dc5a42bc779351bb7659a1608d5a4de3b2","tid":1597924,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"呢個係碎料嚟<br />\n最出名嘅係回歸後阿一懷念英女王所煮嘅<br />\n蘆葦蔥后麵<br />\n連狗都忍唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84643b67447fc443ae723059996fae2d397a2093","tid":1597924,"uid":152482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"蘆葦芯邊度有得賣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1124a0b255ea28f2b592429c521effc6434cbd91","tid":1597924,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84643b67447fc443ae723059996fae2d397a2093","tid":1597924,"uid":152482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"蘆葦芯邊度有得賣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\